|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| Single consolidated per-plan context object handed to subagents | Uniform args include `context_envelope_snapshot`; agents hydrate from `docs/plan/{plan_id}/context_envelope.json` [SOURCE: specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/external/gem-team-main/AGENTS.md:21] | Spec-kit has structured Context Packages and canonical continuity-first retrieval, but not a persisted per-task envelope handed to every subagent [SOURCE: .opencode/agents/context.md:34] [SOURCE: .opencode/agents/context.md:58] | ADAPT | M | Medium-high: use Context Package as dispatch snapshot without replacing packet docs |
| Progressive after-wave enrichment | Orchestrator enriches envelope between waves through documentation writer [SOURCE: specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/external/gem-team-main/AGENTS.md:61] and writes after each wave [SOURCE: specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/external/gem-team-main/AGENTS.md:72] | Spec-kit save path updates packet docs and routes chunks to continuity/handover/research/task surfaces [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/references/memory/save_workflow.md:311] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/references/memory/save_workflow.md:319] | ADAPT | M | Medium: add wave-level refresh discipline for orchestrated multi-agent work |
| In-memory orchestrator cache plus post-wave write to avoid stale reads/races | Orchestrator reads disk once, maintains in-memory cache, writes after updates [SOURCE: specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/external/gem-team-main/AGENTS.md:72] | Spec-kit already serializes canonical saves with a filesystem lock and releases it after workflow completion [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/memory/generate-context.ts:400] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/scripts/memory/generate-context.ts:784] | REJECT | S | Low: equivalent race control exists; extra in-memory authority risks drift from canonical docs |
